nodes.text: A male Green-skinned Trandoshan was a member of the Black Heth criminal gang in 32 BBY. He was part of a group of thugs who took control of Elcor Station in the Coruscant underworld. He carried a large mace at that time. He fought the Jedi Padawan Obi-Wan Kenobi on top of a hovertrain and died in the struggle. Kenobi then cleared a piece of debris blocking the Elcor train, and returned to the Jedi Temple.
The Trandoshan gang member appears in the 2001 video game Star Wars: Obi-Wan. He serves as the boss of the first level.
